  <div class="trac-ticket-buttons">
  </div>
    <div class="comment searchable">
      <p>
This occurs because the {{ and }} are the starting and ending delimiters for variables. This also affects block tag delimters, {% and %}, and comment tag delimiters, {# and #}. In all cases they must be matching. <br />
</p>

    </div>

              </div>
